{"tid":238821,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[An] 單手用語音覆WhatsApp: OneTalk","createTime":"2017-05-11T09:18:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-11T09:52:33.000Z","uid":116024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e4106167e0b5bcdc4856a00754bc3dcb2f405605","tid":238821,"uid":116024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T09:18:01.000Z","msg":"有時唔得閒禁鍵盤覆Message，例如揸車、煮飯、打機既時候，今次介紹既Android App就啱曬喇。<br />\n<br />\nOneTalk係對話懸浮泡泡既Android App，支援大部分即時通訊App。當有人Send Message比你既時候，唔洗開個App，OneTalk就會自動將回覆泡泡放喺屏幕邊緣，撳一下個泡泡就可以用語音輸入或鍵盤打字。<br />\n<br />\nApp名稱：OneTalk<br />\n支援系統：Android<br />\n支援IM：WhatsApp、LINE、Messenger、Telegram、Hangouts、Between、KakaoTalk<br />\n特色功能：單手覆機泡、廣東話語音輸入、自動讀Message<br />\n下載鏈接：<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.onetalkapp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.onetalkapp&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=e783c0af\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.onetalkapp</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">詳細介紹</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n1. 支援大部分主流的即時通訊（IM）軟件，包括WhatsApp、LINE、Messenger、Telegram、Hangouts、Between（啱曬用黎覆男/女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）、KakaoTalk<br />\n<strong><img src=\"https://blog.3bro.info/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/onetalk-1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.3bro.info%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2Fonetalk-1.png&h=ad20a5f5&s={SIZE}\" /></strong><br />\n2a. 訊息到個陣就會喺屏幕邊緣都浮個泡出黎，撳一下就可以用語音輸入（支援廣東話、普通話、英文）回覆，亦可改做撳一下用鍵盤覆。<br />\n<strong><img src=\"https://blog.3bro.info/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/onetalk-2a-e1494444121262.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.3bro.info%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2Fonetalk-2a-e1494444121262.png&h=ca24ac76&s={SIZE}\" /></strong><br />\n2b. 撳一下後，就可以用語音打字，OneTalk會辨認你講既句子同轉換做文字。<br />\n<strong><img src=\"https://blog.3bro.info/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/onetalk-2b-e1494444191194.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.3bro.info%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2Fonetalk-2b-e1494444191194.png&h=3fb24c10&s={SIZE}\" /></strong><br />\n2c. 如果認錯字既話，就可以撳修改制，自己改錯別字。<br />\n<strong><img src=\"https://blog.3bro.info/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/onetalk-2c-e1494444204875.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.3bro.info%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2Fonetalk-2c-e1494444204875.png&h=0d88ac1f&s={SIZE}\" /></strong><br />\n3a. 長撳個泡就可以揀快速回覆既短句（可以喺設定入面改）<br />\n<strong><img src=\"https://blog.3bro.info/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/onetalk-3a-e1494444226257.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.3bro.info%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2Fonetalk-3a-e1494444226257.png&h=ae9d82bd&s={SIZE}\" /></strong><br />\n3b. 筆者改咗做：ok、轉頭覆你<br />\n<strong><img src=\"https://blog.3bro.info/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/onetalk-3b-e1494444317166.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.3bro.info%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2Fonetalk-3b-e1494444317166.png&h=adeee86d&s={SIZE}\" /></strong><br />\n4. OneTalk仲有個特別功能，就係自動讀Message：<br />\n喺通知欄開咗個功能之後，一收到訊息，OneTalk就會用文字轉語音既方式讀個訊息內容。<br />\n<strong><img src=\"https://blog.3bro.info/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/onetalk-4a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.3bro.info%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2Fonetalk-4a.png&h=2f905f90&s={SIZE}\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">實際體驗</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">使用情景</span><br />\nOneTalk既用途好廣泛，筆者用咗一個禮拜後，留意到有幾個情況，OneTalk係特別好用：<br />\n<ul>[*]踩單車<br />\n筆者會將手機放喺單車個handlebar度，開咗自動讀Msg既功能後，一有Friend Send Msg畀我，我就可以聽個Msg內容，唔洗掂個mon，冇咁易分心。<br />\n當我想覆既話，撳一下個泡，然後講我想回覆既句子，個Message就會自動Send畀人。[*]打機<br />\n打機個陣，好多時唔得閒覆。用OneTalk就可以輕鬆撳泡覆訊息。[*]煲劇<br />\n唔洗開IM就可以撳泡覆機，唔會擋住個mon，追劇更加方便。</ul><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">語音輸入</span><br />\n對廣東話既辨識度好高，大部分時間都唔洗自己改字，講野個陣加啲停頓就可以插入空白或者標點符號，幾方便。<br />\n<img src=\"https://blog.3bro.info/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/onetalk-5-e1494444351843.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.3bro.info%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2Fonetalk-5-e1494444351843.png&h=7a82ffb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唯一唔夠完美既位，就是OneTalk不支援同時用語音輸入廣東話同英語，而我地平時講野好常見中英夾雜，例如：『MTR又壞車喇』。講呢類句子既時候，就要自己改錯字。<br />\n<br />\n下載Link: <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.onetalkapp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.onetalkapp&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=e783c0af\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.onetalkapp</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">總結</span><br />\nOneTalk係個幾實用既Android App，用完一排發覺好多時都用得著，大家可以留個言，講下你覺得幾時最好用。<br />\n<br />\n利申：3Bro Blog作者，個App係台灣人寫，原本係寫黎自己打機既時候用，最近加咗廣東話語音輸入，所以就搵咗我地幫手宣傳，覺得好用就畀個正評啦。<br />\n<br />\n原文: <a href=\"https://blog.3bro.info/archives/onetalk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.3bro.info%2Farchives%2Fonetalk%2F&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=dab30182\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.3bro.info/archives/onetalk/</a>"},{"pid":"96739c5b3eed4cfa138448de165621490b22f14e","tid":238821,"uid":104664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T09:52:33.000Z","msg":"大家又要準備畀條女問做乜方便到咁都唔覆msg啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}